## Infrastructure

| Component | Purpose | Key constraint |
|---|---|---|
| PostgreSQL + pgvector | OLTP + vector search | RLS on every tenant table |
| Redis | Auth cache, rate limit, hot memory cache | Key format: `{prefix}:{org_id}:{...}` |
| ClickHouse | LLM trace analytics | Append-only, never update |
| MinIO | Session archives | S3-compatible |
| Prometheus | Metrics | No high-cardinality labels |
| OpenTelemetry | Distributed traces | W3C traceparent propagation |

## Naming conventions

### Go
- Packages: `lowercase`, single word where possible (`ratelimit`, not `rate_limit`)
- Interfaces: noun or noun-phrase (`Limiter`, `AgentStore`, not `ILimiter`)
- Errors: `Err` prefix for sentinel values (`ErrNotFound`), typed structs for structured errors
- Context keys: unexported struct types, never strings
- Test functions: `TestUnit_Scenario` (e.g. `TestRedisSlider_ConcurrentBurst`)
- Constructors: `New*` returns the concrete type; caller assigns to interface

### Python
- Modules: `snake_case`
- Classes: `PascalCase`
- Functions/variables: `snake_case`
- Constants: `UPPER_SNAKE_CASE`
- Type aliases: `PascalCase`

### TypeScript
- Components: `PascalCase`
- Hooks: `use` prefix, camelCase
- Utilities: `camelCase`
- Constants: `UPPER_SNAKE_CASE`
- Types/Interfaces: `PascalCase` (no `I` prefix)

### SQL / Migrations
- Tables: `snake_case`, plural (`organizations`, `agents`)
- Columns: `snake_case`
- Indexes: `idx_{table}_{columns}` (e.g. `idx_agents_org_id`)
- Constraints: `{table}_{column}_{type}` (e.g. `agents_slug_format`)
- Migration files: `{6-digit-seq}_{action}_{subject}.{up,down}.sql`

### Proto
- Messages: `PascalCase`
- Fields: `snake_case`
- RPCs: `PascalCase` verb-noun (`ValidateToken`, `ValidateAgent`)
- Packages: `ibex.{service}.v{N}` (e.g. `ibex.auth.v1`)

## Critical path latency budgets (never exceed)

| Operation | Budget |
|---|---|
| Auth `ValidateToken` gRPC | 50ms |
| Auth `ValidateAgent` gRPC | 50ms |
| Redis rate limit check | 5ms |
| Full proxy overhead (not including LLM) | 20ms (p99) |
| DB query (indexed lookup) | 10ms |
| Context assembly (Phase 2) | 40ms |
